    "name": "BonusAssignment API",
    "description": "Postman collection for the BonusAssignment shopping cart total cost calculation endpoint.\n\nMain assignment flow:\n1. Call GET /api/carts/{{cartId}}/total\n2. Verify the response contains the cart total\n3. Demonstrate error handling with a missing cart",
